(109, 17, 'JAMB', 'COMPUTER SCIENCE', '2023', '&lt;p&gt;Which Of The Following Components Of The Computer Is Referred To As The Administrative Section ?&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'CPU  ', ' Output Unit ', 'Input Unit ', 'Memory Unit', '', 'A Explanation CPU is referred to as the administrative section of the computer, it is also called the brain of the computer.   ', 1, '2024-02-14 13:04:01'),
(110, 17, 'JAMB', 'COMPUTER SCIENCE', '2023', '&lt;p&gt;Which Of The Following Is Not A Third Generation Language?&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', ' FORTRAN', 'COBOL', 'Assembly Language', ' Basic', '', 'C Explanation Assembly language is a low-level programming language that is specific to a particular computer architecture. It is more difficult to learn and use than higher-level programming languages, but it offers more control over the hardware.   ', 1, '2024-02-14 13:05:39'),
