(112, 17, 'JAMB', 'COMPUTER SCIENCE', '2023', '&lt;p&gt;The Type Of Database In Which The Data Are Connected In Different Files By Using Common Data Elements Or A Key Field Is ?&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', ' Relational database ', 'Network Database', 'Hierarchical Database ', 'Object-Oriented Database', '', 'A Explanation Relational database connects data in different files by using a common data elements or a key field.   ', 1, '2024-02-14 13:11:54'),
