(132, 17, 'JAMB', 'COMPUTER SCIENCE', '2023', '&lt;p&gt;Which Of The Following Does Not Replicate Itself In An Infected Computer?&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'spyware  ', 'Worm', 'Trojan Horse', 'Virus', '', 'C Explanation trojan horse is a malicious software program that hides inside other programs, trojan horse does not usually spread by themselves.', 1, '2024-02-14 14:06:12'),
(133, 17, 'JAMB', 'COMPUTER SCIENCE', '2023', '&lt;p&gt;The Last Cycle Of Data Processing Where Data And Information Are Preserved For Future Is Called&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', ' processing', 'Recording', 'Storage', 'Output', '', 'C Explanation The last cycle of data processing where data and information are preserved for future use is called &apos;storage&apos;. This is the phase where data or information is saved either temporarily or permanently for future use. The &apos;output&', 1, '2024-02-14 14:08:20'),
(134, 17, 'JAMB', 'COMPUTER SCIENCE', '2023', '&lt;p&gt;A Device That Sends And Receives Printed Pages Or Images Over Telephone Lines By Digitizing The Material With An Internal Optical Scanner And Transmitting The Information As Electronic Signals Is A&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'A.Â ATM ', 'scanner ', 'C.Â GSM', 'fax machine', '', 'D Explanation Fax machine is a device that sends and receives printed pages or images over telephone lines by digitizing the material with an internal optical scanner and transmitting the information as electronic signals.', 1, '2024-02-14 14:10:31'),
