(136, 17, 'JAMB', 'COMPUTER SCIENCE', '2023', '&lt;p&gt;An Action Performed In The GUI Operating Systems To Hide A Window But Keep The Program Running In The Background Is ?&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'hide ', 'multitasking ', 'minimize', 'maximize', '', 'C Explanation Minimize is an action performed in the GUI operating systems to hide a window but keep the program running in the background   ', 1, '2024-02-14 14:13:23'),
