(570, 17, 'JAMB', 'ENGLISH LANGUAGE', '2023', '&lt;p&gt;From The Novel;&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a Href=&quot;https://myschool.ng/classroom/novels/the-life-changer&quot; Target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;The Life Changer&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;This Question Is Based On &amp;quot;The Life Changer&amp;quot; Novel.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nSalma Was Looking More Stunning On The Last Day Of Her Exams Because_______&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'her classmates had planned to go to the beach after the exam ', 'Her Classmates Had Organized A Mini Picnic To Wrap Up The Good Work', 'Â All Of The Above', 'Her Classmates Had Planned A Photo Shoot With Some Lecturers', '', 'D Explanation Self-explanatory', 0, '2024-03-07 09:55:19'),
