(698, 17, 'JAMB', 'CHRISTIAN RELIGIOUS KNOWLEDGE(CRK)', '2023', '&lt;p&gt;Where Did Peter Make The &amp;quot;Great Confession&amp;quot;?&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Near the Sea of Galilee ', 'At The Last Supper ', 'At The Foot Of The Cross', 'Â In The Garden Of Gethsemane', '', 'A Explanation Peter made the &apos;Great Confession&apos; near the Sea of Galilee. This event is recorded in Matthew 16:13-20, Mark 8:27-30, and Luke 9:18-21. Peter confesses that Jesus is the Christ, the Son of the living God, a pivotal moment in the Gos', 0, '2024-03-12 13:21:18'),
