(762, 17, 'JAMB', 'GEOGRAPHY', '2023', '&lt;p&gt;The Largest Ocean In The World Is The&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Arctic ocean ', 'Atlantic Ocean ', 'Indian Ocean ', 'Pacific Ocean', '', 'D Explanation The Pacific Ocean is the largest ocean in the world. It is larger than all of the Earth&apos;s land area combined. The other options, the Atlantic Ocean, Indian Ocean, and Arctic Ocean, are smaller in comparison.', 0, '2024-03-13 11:13:50'),
(763, 17, 'JAMB', 'GEOGRAPHY', '2023', '&lt;p&gt;The Type Of Energy That Is Most Environmentally Friendly Is&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Thermal ', 'Nuclear ', 'Hydro Electric', 'Solar', '', 'D Explanation Solar energy is considered the most environmentally friendly type of energy. This is because it is a renewable source of energy that does not emit any greenhouse gases during production. Solar panels can be installed on rooftops, which does ', 0, '2024-03-13 11:15:25'),
(764, 17, 'JAMB', 'GEOGRAPHY', '2023', '&lt;p&gt;Rocks Are Said To Be Crystalline When The Atoms Forming Them Are&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Â found in sedimentary rocks  ', 'Â Found In Crystalline Rocks ', 'Arrenged In A Deposit Pattern', 'Arranged Vertically', '', 'C Explanation Crystalline rocks are rocks that; -do not contain fossils -do not occur in layers i.e they are non-stratified', 0, '2024-03-13 11:16:44'),
(765, 17, 'JAMB', 'GEOGRAPHY', '2023', '&lt;p&gt;The Coastal Regions Of Sierra Leone Record An Annual Rainfall Of Over&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', '3000mm', '6,500mm', '4,800mm', '5,000mm', '', 'C Explanation The annual rainfall in sierra leone coastal regions is over 4,800m, which makes it the wettest country in West Africa', 0, '2024-03-13 11:19:33'),
(766, 17, 'JAMB', 'GEOGRAPHY', '2023', '&lt;p&gt;Which Of The Following Pairs Of Landforms Can Be Found In The Desert Areas?&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Barchans and tombolos ', 'Zeugens And Rock Pedestals ', 'Sauddoars And Tombolos ', 'Yardangs And Batholiths', '', 'B Explanation Zeugens: These are tabular masses with a layer of soft rock lying beneath layer of hard rock Rock pedestals: It consist of horizontal layer of hard and soft rocks', 0, '2024-03-13 11:21:14'),
(767, 17, 'JAMB', 'GEOGRAPHY', '2023', '&lt;p&gt;Which Of The Following Sources Of Power Supply Is Renewable?&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'gas ', 'Nuclear ', 'Solar', 'Cone', '', 'D Explanation Solar energy is the energy gotten from the sun. The sun is the largest (star and its also the ultimate source of light and energy to all the planets. Coal, gas and Nuclear energy are hot renewable(i.e they cannot be reused when exhausted)   ', 0, '2024-03-13 11:22:38'),
(768, 17, 'JAMB', 'GEOGRAPHY', '2023', '&lt;p&gt;Which Of The Following Is Not Correct About The Great Circle?&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'The Equator is a Great Circle among the latitudes ', 'The Greenwich Meridian And The International Date Line Are The Only Lines Of Latitude Forming A Great Circle', 'The Great Circle Divides The Earth Into Two Equal Spheres', 'The Centre Of The Great Circle Is Also The Centre Of The Earth', '', 'B Explanation Great Circles: -A great circle is any line thatdivides the earth into two hemispheres -The center of the Great circle is the center of the earth -Equator is the only line of latitude that is a great circle   ', 0, '2024-03-13 11:24:18'),
(769, 17, 'JAMB', 'GEOGRAPHY', '2023', '&lt;p&gt;The Main Reason For Which Most Manufacturing Industries In West Africa Are Concentrated In Cities And Towns Along The Coast Is That They Have&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'a large number of warehouses ', 'Large Urban Market', 'A Large Pool Of Unskilled Labour ', 'Numerous Banks', '', 'A Explanation This is due to the fact that there is a large number of warehouses in these regions. These warehouses are storage facilities where the goods are kept prior or after shipping.', 0, '2024-03-13 11:26:24'),
(770, 17, 'JAMB', 'GEOGRAPHY', '2023', '&lt;p&gt;The Type Of Agriculture In Which Water Is Conserved In A Year So That Crops Can Be Grown In Succeeding Years By Ploughing, Mulching Or Harrowing Is Known As&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Â arable farming ', 'Â Intensive Cultivation', 'Extensive Cultivation ', 'Dry Farming', '', ' D Explanation Dry farming is a type of agriculture in which water is conserved in a year, particularly during dry season. It is often described as crop production without irrigation   ', 0, '2024-03-13 11:27:51'),
(771, 17, 'JAMB', 'GEOGRAPHY', '2023', '&lt;p&gt;One Of The Features Of Wind Deposition Is&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'a mesa ', 'An Inselberg', 'A Ventifact', 'Barchan', '', 'B Explanation Inselberg is formed from the existence of extensive old plateau. It is caused as a result of weathering and remval of weathered materials', 0, '2024-03-13 11:29:30'),
(772, 17, 'JAMB', 'GEOGRAPHY', '2023', '&lt;p&gt;Which Of The Following Stations Is Situated In A Region Of Tropical Monsoon Climate?&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Valencia ', 'In Salah ', 'Bombay(Munbai) ', 'Durban', '', ' C Explanation Bombay (Mumbai) is located in a region of tropical monsoon climate. A tropical monsoon climate is characterized by high temperatures throughout the year and a significant amount of rainfall, usually in the form of a pronounced wet season. B', 0, '2024-03-13 11:31:29'),
(773, 17, 'JAMB', 'GEOGRAPHY', '2023', '&lt;p&gt;The Instrument Used To Measure The Duration Of Sunshine Is The&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'campbell-stokes recorder ', 'Cup-Anemometer', 'Aneroid Barometer', 'Aneroid Barometer', '', ' A Explanation The direction of sunshine is measured using either campbell-stokes recorder or modern sunshine sensor.', 0, '2024-03-13 11:33:03'),
(774, 17, 'JAMB', 'GEOGRAPHY', '2023', '&lt;p&gt;The Land-use Activities Which Can Be Considered Responsible For Soil Erosion In The Tropics Are&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'irrigation, terrace farming and crop rotation ', 'Mining, Bush Fallowing And Market Gardening ', 'Industrialization, Monoculture And Lumbering ', 'Bush Fallowing, Overgrazing And Monoculture', '', 'C Explanation Industrial activities such as production, construction etc, monoculture and lumbering are responsible for erosion in the tropics', 0, '2024-03-13 11:34:46'),
(775, 17, 'JAMB', 'GEOGRAPHY', '2023', '&lt;p&gt;The Sun Is Vertically Overhead At The Tropic Of Caprison In&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'September 23rd ', 'March 21st', 'June 21st', 'December 22nd', '', 'D Explanation On December 22nd, the sun is overhead at the Tropic of Capricon, resulting in December winter solstice which means that the southern hemisphere will have its longest day and shortest night', 0, '2024-03-13 11:36:20'),
(776, 17, 'JAMB', 'GEOGRAPHY', '2023', '&lt;p&gt;Barchan Dunes Move&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Â at right angle to the prevailing wind ', 'In The Same Direction As The Prevailing Winds ', 'In The Same Direction As The Prevailing Winds ', 'In A Circular Direction', '', ' A Explanation A barchan is a cresentic or moon-shaped structure. A barchan is formed when an obstacle like rocks impedes or prevents the movement of wind', 0, '2024-03-13 11:40:04'),
(777, 17, 'JAMB', 'GEOGRAPHY', '2023', '&lt;p&gt;The Major Crop Grown In The El Juf Basin Of Mali Is&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Cotton ', 'Cashew ', 'Cocoa ', 'Coffee', '', ' A Explanation Agriculture is the dominant economic sector in the country of Mali. In El-Djoul basin, cotton production is very commonly practiced   ', 0, '2024-03-13 11:42:37'),
(778, 17, 'JAMB', 'GEOGRAPHY', '2023', '&lt;p&gt;What Is The Temperature Around An Aeroplane Flying At An Altitude Of 4000metres If The Temperature On The Earth&amp;#39;s Surface Is&amp;nbsp;40&amp;ordm;c40&amp;ordm;ï¿½?&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', '140C', '660C', '260C', '(\\12^0C\\)', '', 'A Explanation Lapse rate is simply described as 0.65Â°C per 100m of ascent or 6.5ÂºC per 1000m of ascent. Therefore 4000m of ascent= 6.5ÂºC x 4000m/1000m=26.0ÂºC Then, the temperature around the aeroplane is = 40ÂºC - 26ÂºC = 14Â°C   ', 0, '2024-03-13 11:44:34'),
(779, 17, 'JAMB', 'GEOGRAPHY', '2023', '&lt;p&gt;A Block Mountain Is Formed As A Result Of&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Â fission ', 'Vulcanisity ', 'Differential Erosion', 'Faulting', '', 'D Explanation Block mountains are formed as a result of lateral or vertical earth movement. They are also formed when the earth cracks due to faulting. Faulting may result from tensional forces or compressional forces.', 0, '2024-03-13 11:46:25'),
(780, 17, 'JAMB', 'GEOGRAPHY', '2023', '&lt;p&gt;Quartz, Fieldspar And Mica Are Three Principal Mineral That Can Easily Be Seen In&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'limestone ', 'Basalt', 'Coal', 'Granite', '', 'D Explanation Granite is an example of heterogenous rock that contains a mixture of the minerals quartz, mica and fieldspar and is variable in colour', 0, '2024-03-13 11:48:39'),
(781, 17, 'JAMB', 'GEOGRAPHY', '2023', '&lt;p&gt;The Difference In Time Between Two Longitudes Is Approximately&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', '15 hours ', '4 Hours', '40 Minutes', '4 Minutes', '', 'D Explanation The Earth is divided into 360 degrees of longitude, so every degree of longitude is equal to 4 minutes of time. This is because there are 24 hours in a day and 360 divided by 24 is 15. Therefore, the difference in time between two longitudes', 0, '2024-03-13 11:49:57'),
(782, 17, 'JAMB', 'GEOGRAPHY', '2023', '&lt;p&gt;The Dam Which Is Not Used In Gezira Is The&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Aswan ', 'Jebal Azula', 'Jebal Azula', 'Sennar', '', 'C Explanation Jebal Azula is a dam which is not used in Gezira scheme', 0, '2024-03-13 11:52:04'),
(783, 17, 'JAMB', 'GEOGRAPHY', '2023', '&lt;p&gt;The Most Common Form Of Migration Experienced In Countries Of Tropical Africa Is&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'urban-rural migration ', 'Rural-Rural Migration ', 'Urban-Urban Migration ', 'Rural-Urban Migration', '', 'D Explanation Countries in Tropical Africa often experienced rural-urban migration i.e the movement from rural to an urban settlement.', 0, '2024-03-13 11:53:31'),
(784, 17, 'JAMB', 'GEOGRAPHY', '2023', '&lt;p&gt;A Slope Is Said To Be Even When The Contours Are&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'concentric ', 'Â Irregularly Spaced ', 'Closely Spaced ', 'Â Equally Placed', '', 'D Explanation Even or uniform slope is a slope in which its contour line is uniformly spaced. It means, the degree of steepness is the same throughout the slopes   ', 0, '2024-03-13 11:55:08'),
(785, 17, 'JAMB', 'GEOGRAPHY', '2023', '&lt;p&gt;Which Of The Following Distinguishes Rotation From Revolution?&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Revolution causes day and night while rotation causes season ', 'Rotation Causes Variation In The Lengths Of Day And Night While Revolution Causes Rising And Falling Of Tides ', 'A Complete Revolution Takes 24 Hours While Rotation Makes A Year ', 'The Earth Rotates On Its Axis While It Revolves Around The Sun In An Elliptical Orbit', '', 'D Explanation ROTATION,REVOLUTION i. earth rotates on its axis,the earth revolves in an elliptical orbit ii. it causes day and night and takes 24hrs,it causes season and makes a year', 0, '2024-03-13 11:57:12'),
(786, 17, 'JAMB', 'GEOGRAPHY', '2023', '&lt;p&gt;Countries In The Northern Hemisphere Experience Shorter Days And Longer Nights When The Sun Is Overhead On The&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Equator ', 'Artic Circle', 'Tropic Of Cancer', 'Tropic Of Capricorn', '', 'C Explanation On June 21, the sun is overhead at the tropic of cancer, resulting in June or summer scistics', 0, '2024-03-13 11:59:02'),
(787, 17, 'JAMB', 'GEOGRAPHY', '2023', '&lt;p&gt;A Piece Of Evidence That Confirms That The Earth Is Spherical Is&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'solar system ', 'Earth&apos;s Orbit', 'Moon&apos;s Eclipse', 'Standard Time', '', 'C Explanation Evidence of the earth&apos;s sphericity -circumarigation of the earth -lunar eclipse(eclipse of the moon) -sunrise and sunset -ship visibility -the circular horizon', 0, '2024-03-13 12:00:30'),
(788, 17, 'JAMB', 'GEOGRAPHY', '2023', '&lt;p&gt;A Tremendous Pressure Or Temperature Change May Lead To The Formation Of&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'gnesis ', 'Clay ', 'Limestone', 'Granite', '', 'A Explanation Gnesis is a metamorphic rock. Metamorphic rocks are formed from pre-existing rocks which have been changed as a result of great heat and pressure', 0, '2024-03-13 12:02:02'),
(789, 17, 'JAMB', 'GEOGRAPHY', '2023', '&lt;p&gt;Exports From Mali Are Most Likely To Pass Through The Sea Port At&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Banjul ', 'Abidjan', 'Lagos', 'Dakar', '', 'B Explanation Traditionally, Abidjan in Cote d&apos; Ivoire has been Mali&apos;s main seaport, handling as much as 70 percent of Mali&apos;s trade (except for gold export)', 0, '2024-03-13 12:03:44'),
(790, 17, 'JAMB', 'ACCOUNTS-PRINCIPLES OF ACCOUNTS', '2023', '&lt;p&gt;The Following Are Importance Of Branch Account Except&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'it allows fraud and wastage of resources ', 'It Assist The Organization To Determine The Performance Of A Branch Manager', 'It Enable The Organization To Determine The Branch That Is Making Either Profit Or Loss ', 'Â It Allows Proper Control Over The Branch By The Head Office', '', 'A Explanation The importance and objectives of branch account are: - to access the performance of the branches - to prevent wastage - to prevent fraud and other malpractices - to ascertain the profit or loss for each branch', 0, '2024-03-19 08:53:05'),
(791, 17, 'JAMB', 'ACCOUNTS-PRINCIPLES OF ACCOUNTS', '2023', '&lt;p&gt;The Use Of Three Column Cash Book Is Determined By&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'trade discount ', 'Cash Transaction', 'Bank Transaction', 'Cash Discount', '', 'D Explanation The cash discount is allowed for prompt payment of an account or for payment within a specified period of time. It is divided into discount allowed and discount received.', 0, '2024-03-19 08:54:27'),
(792, 17, 'JAMB', 'ACCOUNTS-PRINCIPLES OF ACCOUNTS', '2023', '&lt;p&gt;The Authority Warrant Issued Prior To The Approval Of The Appropriate Bill At The Begining Of The Year&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'contigencies ', 'Reserved Expenditure Warrant', 'Annual General Warrant ', 'Â Provisional General Warrant', '', 'D Explanation Provisional general warrant is used to release fund for the payment of emolument and other services before the budget is approved. It will be in operation for four months.', 0, '2024-03-19 08:55:50'),
(793, 17, 'JAMB', 'ACCOUNTS-PRINCIPLES OF ACCOUNTS', '2023', '&lt;table Border=&quot;1&quot; Cellpadding=&quot;1&quot; Cellspacing=&quot;1&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;tbody&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;td&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td&gt;\r\n			&lt;p&gt;â‚¦&lt;/p&gt;\r\n			&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;td&gt;\r\n			&lt;p&gt;Debtors Opening&lt;/p&gt;\r\n			&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td&gt;4000&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;td&gt;Debtors Closing&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td&gt;1500&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;td&gt;\r\n			&lt;p&gt;Cash Received From Debtors&lt;/p&gt;\r\n			&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td&gt;8500&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;td&gt;\r\n			&lt;p&gt;Bad Debts Written Off&lt;/p&gt;\r\n			&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td&gt;350&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;td&gt;Discount Allowed&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td&gt;500&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;td&gt;Discount Received&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td&gt;1000&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n	&lt;/tbody&gt;\r\n&lt;/table&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;What Is The Amount Of Sales For The Year?&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'â‚¦6850 ', 'â‚¦6650', 'â‚¦3850', 'â‚¦1550', '', 'A Explanation The amount of sales for the year is calculated using the formula: Opening Debtors + Sales - Cash received from debtors - Closing Debtors + Bad debts written off + Discount allowed - Discount received. Plugging in the given values, we get: 40', 0, '2024-03-19 09:06:16'),
(794, 17, 'JAMB', 'ACCOUNTS-PRINCIPLES OF ACCOUNTS', '2023', '&lt;p&gt;The Principle Of Double Entry Developed From The Axioms Of Accounting Equation Is Given As&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Â Liabilties + Equity = Net assets ', 'Assets + Equity = Liabilities', 'Liabilities + Equity = Assets ', 'Assets + Liability = Equity', '', 'C Explanation The accounting equation states that: - Capital( Equity) = Assets - Liabilities - Assets = Capital (Equity) - Liabilties - Liabilties = Assets - Capital (Equity) - Equity(Capital ) = Assets', 0, '2024-03-19 09:09:25'),
(795, 17, 'JAMB', 'ACCOUNTS-PRINCIPLES OF ACCOUNTS', '2023', '&lt;p&gt;A Part Of Public Company&amp;#39;s Profit Belonging To The Shareholders Is&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'right issue ', 'Bonus ', 'Dividends ', 'Â Public Issue', '', 'C Explanation Dividends are a part of a public company&apos;s profit that is distributed to shareholders. It is a way for companies to distribute a portion of their earnings back to their shareholders. Public issue, bonus, and right issue are not parts of', 0, '2024-03-19 09:12:25'),
(796, 17, 'JAMB', 'ACCOUNTS-PRINCIPLES OF ACCOUNTS', '2023', '&lt;p&gt;Accounting Entry For Dissolution Expenses Is&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Dr : Partnership account ;Cr: Realization account ', 'Â Dr: Revaluation Account; Cr: Partnership Account ', 'Dr: Realization Account; Cr: Cash Account', 'Dr: Partners Current Account; Cr: Realization Account', '', ' C Explanation When dissolution expenses are paid, the Realization account is debited because it represents the expenses related to the dissolution of the partnership. The Cash account is credited because cash is going out of the business to pay for these', 0, '2024-03-19 09:14:07'),
(797, 17, 'JAMB', 'ACCOUNTS-PRINCIPLES OF ACCOUNTS', '2023', '&lt;p&gt;One Of The Options Below Is Not The Source Of Income For Non - Profit Organization&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'ordinary shares', 'Donations ', 'Subscription/Dues', 'Entrance Fees', '', 'C Explanation Subscription is the contribution made by the members to the club or society at regular intervals. It can be paid by members in advance or in arrears.', 0, '2024-03-19 09:16:40'),
(798, 17, 'JAMB', 'ACCOUNTS-PRINCIPLES OF ACCOUNTS', '2023', '&lt;p&gt;Which Of These Is The Main Source Document For Recording Cash Paid Into Bank?&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Â invoice ', 'Credit Note', 'Cheque Book', 'Pay-In-Slip', '', 'D Explanation A pay-in-slip is a bank deposit that is used to deposit money into a bank account. It includes information such as date, account number, amount to be paid etc.', 0, '2024-03-19 09:17:51');
