(819, 17, 'JAMB', 'ACCOUNTS-PRINCIPLES OF ACCOUNTS', '2023', '&lt;p&gt;When Expenses Are Paid On Behalf Of The Venture, The Accounting Entries Is To Debit&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'expenses account and credit bank account ', 'Bank Account And Credit Joint Venture Account ', 'Joint Venture Account And Credit Bank Account', 'Joint Venture Account And Credit Expenses Account', '', 'C Explanation Expenditure paid on bahalf of joint venture Accountint entries: Dr: Joint venture account Cr: Bank account   ', 0, '2024-03-19 10:06:08'),
(820, 17, 'JAMB', 'ACCOUNTS-PRINCIPLES OF ACCOUNTS', '2023', '&lt;p&gt;The Discount Column On The Left-hand Side Of Cash Book Represents A Discount&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Â received from a debtor  ', 'Allowed To A Creditor', 'Allowed To A Debtor ', 'Â Received From A Creditor', '', 'C Explanation The discount on the left hand side is known as discount allowed and it is given by a firm to its customers when they pay their accounts quickly or promptly.', 0, '2024-03-19 10:07:26'),
(821, 17, 'JAMB', 'ACCOUNTS-PRINCIPLES OF ACCOUNTS', '2023', '&lt;p&gt;Goodwill Can Be Introduced When&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'the business suffers high loss ', 'The Business Is Being Expanded', 'The Partnership Experience Super Profit', 'Â A New Member Is Admitted', '', 'D Explanation The circumstances giving rise to the ascertainment of goodwill are: - admission of a new partner - change in profit sharing ratio - death or retirement of a partner - the business has been purchased - dissolution of a business', 0, '2024-03-19 10:08:45'),
(822, 17, 'JAMB', 'ACCOUNTS-PRINCIPLES OF ACCOUNTS', '2023', '&lt;p&gt;Which Fund Is Used To Meet Unforeseen Or Urgent Expenditure&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'special fund ', 'Â Contigencies Fund ', 'General Reserve Fund', 'Consolidated Reserve Fund', '', 'B Explanation Contigency fund is established by the constitution of 1979 to take care of any nation disaster or unforeseen circumstances.', 0, '2024-03-19 10:10:29'),
(823, 17, 'JAMB', 'ACCOUNTS-PRINCIPLES OF ACCOUNTS', '2023', '&lt;p&gt;Given:&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nI. Settlement Of Debts&lt;br /&gt;\r\nII. Cessation Of Business&lt;br /&gt;\r\nIII. Introduction Of Assets&lt;br /&gt;\r\nIV. Disposal Of Assets&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nWhich Of These Constitutes Dissolution Of Partnership?&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Â I,II and III only  ', 'I,II And IV Only ', 'II And IV Only ', 'II And III And IV Only', '', 'B Explanation Bankruptcy of a partner, illegality of object of the business, expiration of the time given, non performance of the business, admission of a new partner, withdrawal or retirement of partners give rise to dissolution of partnership.', 0, '2024-03-19 10:12:00'),
(824, 17, 'JAMB', 'ACCOUNTS-PRINCIPLES OF ACCOUNTS', '2023', '&lt;p&gt;Bello Withdraws Cash From Bank To Office, This Is Called ---------- Entry&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'credit ', 'Contra ', 'Double', 'Debit', '', 'B Explanation Contra entry is an entry which is recorded to reverse or offset an entry on the other side of an account. If a debit entry is recorded in an account, it will be recorded on the credit side and vice-versa.', 0, '2024-03-19 10:13:16'),
(825, 17, 'JAMB', 'ACCOUNTS-PRINCIPLES OF ACCOUNTS', '2023', '&lt;p&gt;Which Of The Following Is Recorded In The Folio Column Of The Journal?&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'particulars of transactions ', 'Date Of Entries ', 'All Credit And Cash Sales Transactions', 'Amount Of Money Posted', '', 'A Explanation The folio shows the page of a ledger to which a transactions is posted. It also helps in identifying where the transaction is recorded in ledger.', 0, '2024-03-19 10:14:36'),
