(921, 17, 'JAMB', 'MATHEMATIC', '2022', '&lt;p&gt;If 299&amp;nbsp;x (Y3)99&amp;nbsp;= 355&amp;nbsp;x (Y3)55, Find The Value Of Y.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', '4', '3 ', '2', '1', '', 'D Explanation (2 x 9 0  ) (Y x 9 1 + 3 x 90 ) = (3 x 5 0 )(Y x 51  + 3 x 50 ).  (2 * 1)(Y *9 + 3) = (3 * 1)(Y * 5 + 3) 18y + 6 = 15y + 9   18y - 15y = 9 - 6   3y = 3  y = 1', 0, '2024-03-21 10:47:47'),
