(941, 17, 'JAMB', 'MATHEMATIC', '2022', '&lt;p&gt;What Is The Derivative Of T2&amp;nbsp;sin (3t - 5) With Respect To T?&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Â 6t cos (3t - 5) ', '2t Sin (3t - 5) - 3t2Â Cos (3t - 5)', '2t Sin (3t - 5) + 3t2Â Cos (3t - 5)', '2t Sin (3t - 5) + T2Â Cos 3t', '', 'C Explanation t2 sin (3t - 5) = 2t sin ( 3t - 5) + t2 x 3 cos (3t - 5) = 2t sin (3t - 5) + 3t2 cos (3t - 5).', 0, '2024-03-21 11:11:43'),
