(1032, 17, 'JAMB', 'CHRISTIAN RELIGIOUS STUDIES(CRK)', '2022', '&lt;p&gt;What Was Ezekiel Ordered To Eat Before He Went To Speak To The House Of Israel?&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Honey ', 'Locust', 'Bread', 'A Scroll', '', 'D Explanation Ezekiel was told by God that he was to be a prophet to the rebellious Israelites, even though they may refuse to listen to him. God then told Ezekiel: &quot;Open your mouth and eat what I am giving you&quot; (Ez. 2:8), and a scroll was hande', 0, '2024-04-11 18:47:24'),
(1033, 17, 'JAMB', 'CHRISTIAN RELIGIOUS STUDIES(CRK)', '2022', '&lt;p&gt;What Was The Sign Of God&amp;#39;s Covenant With Abraham?&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Smoke ', 'Fire', 'Circumcision', 'Children', '', ' C Explanation The token or sign of the covenant God made with Abraham was circumcision. Circumcision symbolized cleanliness before God and was also a symbolic reminder of the promises the Lord made to Abraham regarding his posterity.', 0, '2024-04-11 18:48:53'),
(1034, 17, 'JAMB', 'CHRISTIAN RELIGIOUS STUDIES(CRK)', '2022', '&lt;p&gt;The Mountain Where Moses Saw The Bush Burning Was Called&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Sinai ', 'Nebo', 'Camel', 'Horeb', '', 'D Explanation The Burning Bush. Now Moses was tending the flock of Jethro his father-in-law, the priest of Midian, and he led the flock to the far side of the desert and came to Horeb, the mountain of God. There the angel of the LORD appeared to him in fl', 0, '2024-04-11 18:50:14'),
(1035, 17, 'JAMB', 'CHRISTIAN RELIGIOUS STUDIES(CRK)', '2022', '&lt;p&gt;Where Was The First Place The Disciples Were Called Christians?&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Jerusalem ', 'Joppa', 'Antioch', 'Damascus', '', 'C Explanation &quot;And it was in Antioch that the disciples were first called Christians...&quot; (Acts 11: 26)', 0, '2024-04-11 18:51:40'),
(1036, 17, 'JAMB', 'CHRISTIAN RELIGIOUS STUDIES(CRK)', '2022', '&lt;p&gt;The Complaints Of The ______ Led To The Appointment Of The Deacons In The Early Church.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Hellenists ', 'Gentiles ', 'Pharisees', 'Saducees', '', 'A Explanation The main problem that led to the appointment of the seven deacons centred around discrimination against the Hellenists in the early church.', 0, '2024-04-11 18:53:00'),
(1037, 17, 'JAMB', 'CHRISTIAN RELIGIOUS STUDIES(CRK)', '2022', '&lt;p&gt;The Laws Given By Moses To The Children Of Israel In Sinai Have Striking Similarities With The&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Rosetta ', 'Code Of Hammurabi', 'Septuagint ', 'Roman Laws', '', 'B Explanation The Book of the Covenant is sometimes called the Law of Moses, but the Book of the Covenant and the Law of Hammurabi used in the Babylonian Empire, seem closely related in the contextual and legal language, so it&apos;s easy to see how the C', 0, '2024-04-11 18:54:21'),
(1038, 17, 'JAMB', 'CHRISTIAN RELIGIOUS STUDIES(CRK)', '2022', '&lt;p&gt;&amp;quot;Walk Before Me, And Be Blameless.&amp;quot; This Statement Was Addressed To Abraham At The Age Of _____&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', '75 ', '99', '100', '80', '', 'B Explanation When Abram was ninety-nine years old, the LORD appeared to him and said, &quot;I am God Almighty; walk before me faithfully and be blameless. (Gen 17:1)', 0, '2024-04-11 18:55:37'),
(1039, 17, 'JAMB', 'CHRISTIAN RELIGIOUS STUDIES(CRK)', '2022', '&lt;p&gt;&amp;#39;But I Will Be With You And You Will Smite The Midianites As One Man...&amp;#39; This Statement Was Addressed By God To&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Moses ', 'Deborah', 'Joshua', 'Gideon', '', 'D Explanation The LORD turned to him and said, &quot;Go in the strength you have and save Israel from the hand of Midian. Am I not sending you?&quot; &quot;Please, my Lord,&quot; Gideon replied, &quot;how can I save Israel? Indeed, my clan is the weakest ', 0, '2024-04-11 18:57:00'),
(1040, 17, 'JAMB', 'CHRISTIAN RELIGIOUS STUDIES(CRK)', '2022', '&lt;p&gt;&amp;#39;Eli, Eli, Lama Sabachthani?&amp;#39; Whose Accounts Recorded These As Jesus&amp;#39; Words At The Ninth Hour?&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'John and Matthew ', 'Luke And Mark ', 'Mark And Matthew', 'Luke And John', '', 'C Explanation (Matthew 27:46) â€“ &quot;And about the ninth hour Jesus cried out with a loud voice, saying, &apos;Eli, Eli, lama sabachthani?&apos; that is, &apos;My God, My God, why have Your forsaken Me?&apos;&quot; (Mark 15:34) â€“ &quot;And at the nin', 0, '2024-04-11 18:58:20'),
(1041, 17, 'JAMB', 'CHRISTIAN RELIGIOUS STUDIES(CRK)', '2022', '&lt;p&gt;How Many Visions Did Jeremiah See?&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', '1 ', '2', '3', '4', '', 'B Explanation Jeremiah saw a visions of &quot;a branch of an almond tree&quot; (verses 11â€“12) and then a vision of &quot;a boiling pot tilt away from the north&quot; (verses 13â€“16).', 0, '2024-04-11 18:59:56'),
(1042, 17, 'JAMB', 'CHRISTIAN RELIGIOUS STUDIES(CRK)', '2022', '&lt;p&gt;Before The Disciples Casted The Lot And Chos Matthias To Replace Judas Iscariot, The Other Candidate They Had Was?&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Paul ', 'Barnabas', 'Joseph', 'Matthew', '', 'C Explanation The disciples narrowed down the candidates to two people: Joseph (also known as Justus) and a man named Matthias (Acts 1:12-26).', 0, '2024-04-11 19:01:16'),
