(1059, 17, 'JAMB', 'CHRISTIAN RELIGIOUS STUDIES(CRK)', '2022', '&lt;p&gt;God Passed His Message To The People Of Nineveh Through Prophet&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Ezekiel ', 'Jonah', 'Jeremiah', 'Hosea', '', 'B Explanation The prophet Jonah is called by God to go to Nineveh (a great Assyrian city) and prophesy disaster because of the city&apos;s excessive wickedness.', 0, '2024-04-11 19:31:50'),
(1060, 17, 'JAMB', 'CHRISTIAN RELIGIOUS STUDIES(CRK)', '2022', '&lt;p&gt;After The Israelites Complained To Moses And Aaron, What Did The Lord Promise To Feed The Israelites With In The Morning?&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Meat ', 'Fish', 'Bread', 'Nothing', '', 'C Explanation In the evening the Lord will give you flesh to eat, and in the morning bread to the full(Exodus 16:8)', 0, '2024-04-11 19:32:53'),
(1061, 17, 'JAMB', 'CHRISTIAN RELIGIOUS STUDIES(CRK)', '2022', '&lt;p&gt;When Jesus Was Born In Bethlehem, Who Was The King Of Judea?&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Herod Agrippa  ', 'Â Herod The Great', 'Pontius Pilate', 'Herod Antipas', '', 'B Explanation Herod the Great was king of Judea when Jesus was born. Herod did not remain king for long. Within two years of Jesus&apos; birth he was dead. His son did not last long as king either, as he was dismissed as king by Rome, and replaced by Roma', 0, '2024-04-11 19:34:33'),
