(1063, 17, 'JAMB', 'CHRISTIAN RELIGIOUS STUDIES(CRK)', '2022', '&lt;p&gt;__________ Had Christ&amp;#39;s Body Placed In His Own Tomb.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Simon of Cyrene ', 'Joseph Of Judea', 'Pontius Pilate', 'Joseph Of Arimathea', '', 'D Explanation After Jesus&apos; crucifixion, Joseph of Arimathea asked Pilate for Jesus&apos; body (Mark 15:43). His request was granted, and Matthew 27:59-60 says,&quot;Joseph took the body, wrapped it in a clean linen cloth, and placed it in his own new', 0, '2024-04-11 19:37:14');
