(1070, 17, 'JAMB', 'CHRISTIAN RELIGIOUS STUDIES(CRK)', '2022', '&lt;p&gt;_______ Deceitfully Took 150 Pounds Of Silver In Two Bags And Two Changes Of Clothes Against The Wish Of His Master.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Naboth ', 'Judas', 'Gehazi', 'Naaman', '', 'C Explanation (2 Kings 5:1) Elisha the prophet healed Naaman of his leprosy by the power of the Lord (verse 14), and Naaman praised God and offered Elisha a gift, which Elisha refused to accept (verse 16). Naaman departed for Syria, but Elisha&apos;s serv', 0, '2024-04-11 19:47:16'),
