(1074, 17, 'JAMB', 'CHRISTIAN RELIGIOUS STUDIES(CRK)', '2022', '&lt;p&gt;The Penultimate Plague God Put In Egypt Before The Israelites Were Set Free Was&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Â Plague of locust ', 'Plague Of Flies ', 'Plague Of Lice Or Gnats', 'Plague Of Darkness', '', 'D Explanation &quot;Then the Lord said to Moses, &apos;Stretch out your hand toward heaven, that there may be darkness over the land of Egypt, darkness which may even be felt.&apos; So Moses stretched out his hand toward heaven, and there was thick darkne', 0, '2024-04-11 19:53:22'),
(1075, 17, 'JAMB', 'CHRISTIAN RELIGIOUS STUDIES(CRK)', '2022', '&lt;p&gt;Pharaoh&amp;#39;s Horsemen And His Army Overtook The Fleeing Hebrews, Encamped By The Sea, At&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Pihahirot ', 'Succot', 'Etham', 'Migdol', '', 'A Explanation The Egyptians--all Pharaoh&apos;s horses and chariots, horsemen and troops--pursued the Israelites and overtook them as they camped by the sea near Pi Hahiroth, opposite Baal Zephon.', 0, '2024-04-11 19:57:12'),
