(1080, 17, 'JAMB', 'CHRISTIAN RELIGIOUS STUDIES(CRK)', '2022', '&lt;p&gt;In Paul&amp;#39;s Letter To The Romans, All Who Were Baptized Into Christ Were Also Baptized Into His&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Resurrection ', 'Death', 'Salvation', 'Suffering', '', 'B Explanation Romans 6:3 Do you not know that all of us who have been baptized into Christ Jesus were baptized into his death? We were buried therefore with him by baptism into death, in order that, just as Christ was raised from the dead by the glory of ', 0, '2024-04-11 21:36:53'),
(1081, 17, 'JAMB', 'CHRISTIAN RELIGIOUS STUDIES(CRK)', '2022', '&lt;p&gt;Paul Encouraged Philemon To Receive Onesimus As ______.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'repentant slave  ', 'Fellow Worker', 'Child', 'Brother', '', 'D Explanation Paul wrote to Philemon to encourage him to receive Onesimus back as a brother in the gospel without the severe punishments that would usually be inflicted on runaway slaves. Paul even offered to make up any financial loss Onesimus had caused', 0, '2024-04-11 21:39:05'),
