(1088, 17, 'JAMB', 'CHRISTIAN RELIGIOUS STUDIES(CRK)', '2022', '&lt;p&gt;In Paul&amp;#39;s Epistle To The Galatians, As Long As An Heir Is A Child, He Is Under&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Teachers ', 'Guardians', 'Protectors', 'Custodians', '', 'B Explanation Galatians 4. What I am saying is that as long as the heir is a child, he is no different from a slave, although he owns the whole estate. He is subject to guardians and trustees until the time set by his father.', 0, '2024-04-11 21:52:54'),
(1089, 17, 'JAMB', 'CHRISTIAN RELIGIOUS STUDIES(CRK)', '2022', '&lt;p&gt;After His Resurrection,Jesus First Appeared To&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Mary the mother of Jesus ', 'Mary The Mother Of James', 'Mary Magdalene ', 'Peter', '', 'C Explanation Mark 16:9-11 Jesus appears to Mary Magdalene, who is now described as someone whom Jesus healed from possession by seven demons. She then &quot;tells the other disciples&quot; what she saw, but no one believes her.', 0, '2024-04-11 21:56:04'),
