(1098, 17, 'JAMB', 'CHRISTIAN RELIGIOUS STUDIES(CRK)', '2022', '&lt;p&gt;Who Accompanied Paul On His First Missionary Journey?&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'Barnabas ', 'Lucius', 'Silas', 'Peter', '', 'A Explanation The first missionary journey began in about 45 A.D. From Antioch, Barnabas and Saul traveled about sixteen miles to the coast, to the port at Seleucia Pieria.', 0, '2024-04-11 22:11:00'),
