(1103, 17, 'JAMB', 'COMPUTER STUDIES', '2022', '&lt;p&gt;A Computer Can&amp;#39;t Boot If It Does Not Have ____________&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'compiler ', 'Loader', 'OS', 'Assembler', '', ' C Explanation The Operating system is responsible for the running of the computer. Hence, in its absence, its impossible for the computer to boot.', 0, '2024-04-12 18:42:14'),
(1104, 17, 'JAMB', 'COMPUTER STUDIES', '2022', '&lt;p&gt;Fire Fox Is An Example Of __________&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'System software ', 'Application Package', 'Application Software', 'Computer Tools.', '', ' C Explanation Fire fox is an application software, because it is not an operating system, hence it can&apos;t be classified as a system software because it doesn&apos;t contribute to the running of the computer system.', 0, '2024-04-12 18:43:32'),
(1105, 17, 'JAMB', 'COMPUTER STUDIES', '2022', '&lt;p&gt;The Caps Key On A Keyboard Is Used To___________&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 'move to previous page ', 'Delete Files', 'Switch Between Upper And Lower Case Letters', 'Space Texts', '', 'C Explanation Caps Lock is a key on a computer keyboard that allows users to generate letters in uppercase once activated, as in &quot;SAMPLE,&quot; without holding down the Shift key. It is a toggle key and can be found on the left side of a computer key', 0, '2024-04-12 18:45:06'),
